            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    日经平均指数初段报53,094.79点，跌488.78点或0.91%。<br/><br/>南韩首尔综合指数初段报4,844.11点，跌60.55点或1.23%。 (WL)</span>\n</div>",
